{"id":1255,"date":"2024-08-04T01:37:23","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T01:37:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1255"},"modified":"2024-08-04T01:37:23","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T01:37:23","slug":"mission-055","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-055\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #055: Splishy Splash"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #055: Splishy Splash<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Redwood Village, Northeast House &#8211; Fisherman inside<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete the main story missions up until Redwood Village<\/li>\n<li>Join the Hip Waders in Seaport City<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Catch 30 Magikarp and put them all in the same Box<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Pok\u00e9mon<\/u>: <strong>Shiny Magikarp<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>In Redwood Village, there\u2019s a Fisherman NPC who wants you to catch 30 Magikarp and put them all in the same Box.<\/p>\n<p>When the mission is complete, the Fisherman will give you a Shiny Magikarp.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-hip-waders-club.jpg\" alt=\"The Hip Waders club \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Hip Waders club<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Before accepting the mission, you\u2019ll need to be a member of the Hip Waders club.<\/p>\n<p>You can join by speaking to the Fisherman in the house next to the Battleground in Seaport City.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-southeast-house-in-redwood-village.jpg\" alt=\"The southeast house in Redwood Village \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The southeast house in Redwood Village<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After you\u2019ve done so, head to Redwood Village.<\/p>\n<p>The house in the southeast corner of Redwood Village has a member of the Hip Waders in it, and he offers a mission to fellow members.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/03-pokemon-unbound-catch-magikarp.jpg\" alt=\"Catch Magikarp \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Catch Magikarp<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Fisherman wants you to catch a total of 30 Magikarp and place them within the same Box in the Pok\u00e9mon Storage System.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/04-pokemon-unbound-fishing-in-dresco-town.jpg\" alt=\"Fishing in Dresco Town \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Fishing in Dresco Town<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Magikarp are caught by using the Old Rod in most bodies of water, though there are some areas where other fish can be caught with the Old Rod as well.<\/p>\n<p>For maximum efficiency, using an Old Rod over and over again in a place like <strong>Dresco Town<\/strong> is the best way of catching 30 Magikarp in a row very quickly. Be sure to stock up on Poke balls first.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/05-pokemon-unbound-filling-the-box.jpg\" alt=\"Filling the Box \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Filling the Box<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you\u2019ve caught 30 Magikarp, go to a PC or a Porygon to make sure they have ended up in the same Box. You can easily move them around if not.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/055\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-shiny-magikarp-reward.jpg\" alt=\"The Shiny Magikarp reward \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Shiny Magikarp reward<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you return to the Fisherman, he will take all 30 Magikarp out of your Box and give you a Shiny Magikarp.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1256,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1255","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1255","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1256"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1255"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1255"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}